#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-11-03-civil-disobedience-examples.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"> *It’s not enough to believe in something. You have to be ready to stand for something, if you want change.* \n"
">\n"
"> *\\- Edward Snowden* \n"
msgstr ""
"> *No es suficiente con creer en ello. Tienes que estar listo para "
